div.p:
Some things went recently to Professor du Bocage
See M to J. Barbosa du Bocage, 5 September 1887 (in this edition as 87-09-05b). in Lisbon as gratitude for the great honour shown me by the court there;
M was appointed Knight Grand Cross of the Portuguese Order of Christ in 1887; see King of Portugal to M, 28 April 1887 (in this edition as 87-04-28a). but in the consignment there is nothing or very little that you lack.
